title: Billy Cobham interview with The Black Page drum magazine
description: Billy Cobham interview with The Black Page drum magazine's Sean Mitchell. Visit us at www.theblackpage.net. Billy Cobham chats with us about his latest album, his life in Switzerland and his drumming prowess at 70 years young!
